<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79a6c41c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2910"><num value="2910">§ 2910.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for purposes of making reimbursements under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s2905">section 2905 of this title</ref> to States for the development and implementation of conservation plans and for administration of this chapter under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s2907">section 2907 of this title</ref> not to exceed $5,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1992, 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996, and 1997.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79a6c41d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/366/s11">Pub. L. 96–366, § 11</ref>, <date date="1980-09-29">Sept. 29, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/1329">94 Stat. 1329</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/99/375">Pub. L. 99–375</ref>, <date date="1986-08-07">Aug. 7, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/803">100 Stat. 803</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/100/653/tVIII/s801">Pub. L. 100–653, title VIII, § 801</ref>, <date date="1988-11-14">Nov. 14, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/3833">102 Stat. 3833</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/593/tI/s106">Pub. L. 101–593, title I, § 106</ref>, <date date="1990-11-16">Nov. 16, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2955">104 Stat. 2955</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/440/tIII/s301">Pub. L. 102–440, title III, § 301</ref>, <date date="1992-10-23">Oct. 23, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/2234">106 Stat. 2234</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id79a6c41e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
